./  ADD  SSI=71300390,NAME=IGFPNSAV
         TITLE ' IGFPNSAV: NUCLEUS AREA PAGEOUT                        *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IGFPNSAV CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IGFPNSAV  77.130'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00013000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0001 00014000
         GETMAIN  R,LV=(0)                                              00015000
         LR    @10,@01                                             0001 00016000
         USING @DATD,@10                                           0001 00017000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                      0001 00018000
         LM    @00,@01,20(@13)                                     0001 00019000
         ST    @10,8(,@13)                                         0001 00020000
         LR    @13,@10                                             0001 00021000
      SETLOCK OBTAIN,TYPE=LOCAL,MODE=UNCOND,REGS=USE,                  X00022000
               RELATED=(NONE,'NEXT RELEASE LOCK')                       00023000
*   BLKKEY=0;                                                      0033 00024000
         SLR   BLKKEY,BLKKEY                                       0033 00025000
*   PVTPTR=CVTPVTP;                 /* GET PVT ADDRESS               */ 00026000
         L     @14,CVTPTR                                          0034 00027000
         L     PVTPTR,CVTPVTP(,@14)                                0034 00028000
*   START=0;                        /* SET FIRST NUCLEUS PAGE TO   0035 00029000
*                                      PROCESS                       */ 00030000
         SLR   START,START                                         0035 00031000
*   DO WHILE START<CVTNUCB;         /* CVTNUCB=1ST PAGE NOT IN     0036 00032000
*                                      NUCLEUS                       */ 00033000
         B     @DE00036                                            0036 00034000
@DL00036 DS    0H                                                  0037 00035000
*     R1=START;                     /* INPUT TO IEAVFP               */ 00036000
         LR    R1,START                                            0037 00037000
*     CALL IEAVFP;                  /* LOCATE PAGE'S XPTE            */ 00038000
         L     @15,PVTPFP(,PVTPTR)                                 0038 00039000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0038 00040000
*     IF RETCODE=0 THEN                                            0039 00041000
         LTR   RETCODE,RETCODE                                     0039 00042000
         BNZ   @RF00039                                            0039 00043000
*       DO;                         /* IF XPTE FOUND DO FOLLOWING:   */ 00044000
*         XPTEPTR=R1;               /* GET XPTE ADDRESS RETURNED     */ 00045000
         LR    XPTEPTR,R1                                          0041 00046000
*         XPTLSID='FFFFFFFF'X;      /* SET IEAVOUT INTERFACE         */ 00047000
         MVC   XPTLSID(4,XPTEPTR),@CF01516                         0042 00048000
*         BLKADR=START;             /* RESET KEY OF 1ST 2K           */ 00049000
         LR    BLKADR,START                                        0043 00050000
*         GEN( SSK BLKKEY,BLKADR);  /* BLOCK TO ZERO.                */ 00051000
          SSK BLKKEY,BLKADR                                             00052000
*         BLKADR=START+2048;        /* RESET KEY TO 2ND 2K           */ 00053000
         LA    BLKADR,2048                                         0045 00054000
         ALR   BLKADR,START                                        0045 00055000
*         GEN( SSK BLKKEY,BLKADR);  /* BLOCK TO ZERO                 */ 00056000
          SSK BLKKEY,BLKADR                                             00057000
*       END;                        /* END OF XPTE FOUND             */ 00058000
*     ELSE                                                         0048 00059000
*       ;                           /* START/END XPTE NOT FOUND      */ 00060000
@RF00039 DS    0H                                                  0049 00061000
*     START=START+4096;             /* BUMP TO NEXT NUCLEUS PAGE     */ 00062000
         AH    START,@CH01518                                      0049 00063000
*   END;                            /* END NUCLEUS PAGE XPTES      0050 00064000
*                                      PROCESSING                    */ 00065000
@DE00036 L     @14,CVTPTR                                          0050 00066000
         C     START,CVTNUCB(,@14)                                 0050 00067000
         BL    @DL00036                                            0050 00068000
*   GEN( SETLOCK RELEASE,TYPE=LOCAL,REGS=USE,RELATED=(NONE,'NONE'));    00069000
          SETLOCK RELEASE,TYPE=LOCAL,REGS=USE,RELATED=(NONE,'NONE')     00070000
*   R1=0;                           /* START ADDR OF PAGEOUT         */ 00071000
         SLR   R1,R1                                               0052 00072000
*   R15=CVTNUCB;                    /* END ADDR OF PAGEOUT           */ 00073000
         L     @11,CVTPTR                                          0053 00074000
         L     R15,CVTNUCB(,@11)                                   0053 00075000
*   GEN( PGOUT R,A=(R1),EA=(R15),KEEPREL=Y);/* NUCLEUS AREA PAGEOUT  */ 00076000
          PGOUT R,A=(R1),EA=(R15),KEEPREL=Y                             00077000
*   IF RETCODE¬=0 THEN                                             0055 00078000
         LTR   RETCODE,RETCODE                                     0055 00079000
         BZ    @RF00055                                            0055 00080000
*     DO;                           /* BAD RETURN CODE FROM PAGEOUT     00081000
*                                      DO:                           */ 00082000
*       GENERATE;                                                  0057 00083000
          SETLOCK OBTAIN,TYPE=LOCAL,MODE=UNCOND,REGS=USE,              X00084000
               RELATED=(EXIT,'RELEASE LOCK')                            00085000
*       START=0;                    /* LOOP THROUGH THE              */ 00086000
         SLR   START,START                                         0058 00087000
*       DO WHILE START<CVTNUCB;     /* NUCLEUS XPTES                 */ 00088000
         B     @DE00059                                            0059 00089000
@DL00059 DS    0H                                                  0060 00090000

./  ADD  SSI=71431335,NAME=IGFPSAD0
         TITLE 'IGFPSAD0/IGFPSAE0'                                      00005000
*****************************************************************       00010000
*                                                               *       00020000
* MODULE NAME = IGFPSAD0                                        *       00030000
*                                                               *       00050000
* DESCRIPTIVE NAME = PSA AUTHORIZATION SUPPORT                  *       00100000
*                                                               *       00150000
* COPYRIGHT = NONE                                              *       00200000
*                                                               *       00250000
* STATUS = NEW IN VS/2 R3.7 SU51                               @G51GPLK 00300000
*                                                               *       00350000
* FUNCTION = OBTAINS AND RELEASES PSA UPDATE AUTHORIZATION      *       00400000
**                                                             **       00450000
* NOTES =                                                       *       00500000
*                                                               *       00550000
*    DEPENDENCIES = NONE                                        *       00600000
*                                                               *       00650000
*    RESTRICTIONS = NONE                                        *       00700000
*                                                               *       00750000
*    REGISTER CONVENTIONS = SEE EQUATES                         *       00800000
*                                                               *       00850000
*    PATCH LABEL = NONE                                         *       00900000
*                                                               *       00950000
* MODULE TYPE = CONTROL                                         *       01000000
*                                                               *       01050000
*    PROCESSOR = ASSEMBLER                                      *       01100000
*                                                               *       01150000
*    MODULE SIZE =                                              *       01200000
*                                                               *       01250000
*    ATTRIBUTES = FIXED, DISABLED, KEY 0, SUPERVISOR STATE,     *       01300000
*                 REENTRANT                                     *       01320000
*                                                               *       01340000
* ENTRY POINTS = IGFPSAD0                                       *       01400000
*                                                               *       01450000
*    PURPOSE = OBTAINS PSA UPDATE AUTHORIZATION                 *       01700000
*                                                               *       01750000
*    LINKAGE = REGISTER 15 -- ENTRY POINT ADDRESS               *       01800000
*              REGISTER 14 -- RETURN ADDRESS                    *       01830000
*                                                               *       01900000
*    INPUT = DISABLED, KEY 0, SUPERVISOR STATE PSW              *       01950000
*                                                               *       02000000
* ENTRY POINTS = IGFPSAE0                                       *       02005000
*                                                               *       02010000
*    PURPOSE = RELEASES PSA UPDATE AUTHORIZATION                *       02015000
*                                                               *       02020000
*    LINKAGE = REGISTER 15 -- ENTRY POINT ADDRESS               *       02025000
*              REGISTER 14 -- RETURN ADDRESS                    *       02030000
*                                                               *       02035000
*    INPUT = DISABLED, KEY 0, SUPERVISOR STATE PSW              *       02040000
*                                                               *       02050000

*                                                               *       02400000
*    EXIT-NORMAL = RETURN TO ADDRESS IN REGISTER 14             *       02450000

         ENTRY IGFPSAE0            RELEASE AUTHORIZATION ENTRY          03400000

         SPACE 2                                                        03440000

./  ADD  SSI=70460263,NAME=IGFPTAIM
         TITLE 'IGFPTAIM  -  MCH  ACR  INTERFACE MODULE                *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IGFPTAIM CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IGFPTAIM  76.260'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
     STCK   LRBHDATE(LRBPTR)         TIME STAMP                         00013000
*   BC(8,ACTSET);                   /* BRANCH ON CC = 0              */ 00014000
         BC    8,ACTSET                                            0060 00015000
*   LRBHDATE=LRBHDATE&&LRBHDATE;    /* ZERO TIME STAMP               */ 00016000
         XC    LRBHDATE(4,LRBPTR),LRBHDATE(LRBPTR)                 0061 00017000
*   LRBHTIME=LRBHTIME&&LRBHTIME;                                   0062 00018000
         XC    LRBHTIME(4,LRBPTR),LRBHTIME(LRBPTR)                 0062 00019000
*ACTSET:                                                           0063 00020000
*   ;                                                              0063 00021000
ACTSET   DS    0H                                                  0064 00022000
*   TS(LRBMACT);                    /* CHECK LRB ACTIVE FLAGS        */ 00023000
         TS    LRBMACT(LRBPTR)                                     0064 00024000
*   BC(4,CPUHUNT);                  /* BRANCH ON CC = 1              */ 00025000
         BC    4,CPUHUNT                                           0065 00026000
*   LRBMCLB=0;                      /* ZERO CLOBBER BITS             */ 00027000
         MVI   LRBMCLB(LRBPTR),X'00'                               0066 00028000
*CPUHUNT:                                                          0067 00029000
*   ;                                                              0067 00030000
CPUHUNT  DS    0H                                                  0068 00031000
*   CPUAL=CPUCPUAL;                 /* CPU ONLINE BITS IN HIGH ORDER    00032000
*                                      OF REG                        */ 00033000
         L     @15,CVTPTR                                          0068 00034000
         L     @15,CVTCSD(,@15)                                    0068 00035000
         ICM   CPUAL,15,CPUCPUAL+8(@15)                            0068 00036000
*   DO CPUI=0 TO 15;                                               0069 00037000
         SLR   CPUI,CPUI                                           0069 00038000
@DL00069 DS    0H                                                  0070 00039000
*     IF CPUI¬=PSASPAD              /* IS THIS FAILING CPU           */ 00040000
*       THEN                                                       0070 00041000
         CH    CPUI,PSASPAD                                        0070 00042000
         BE    @RF00070                                            0070 00043000
*       IF CPUAL<0                  /* NO - IS THIS ONE ONLINE       */ 00044000
*         THEN                                                     0071 00045000
         LTR   CPUAL,CPUAL                                         0071 00046000
         BNM   @RF00071                                            0071 00047000
*         DO;                                                      0072 00048000
*           R5=PCCAT00P(CPUI+1);    /* PCCA ADDRESS OF CORRECT     0073 00049000
*                                      PROCESSOR                     */ 00050000
         LR    @15,CPUI                                            0073 00051000
         SLA   @15,2                                               0073 00052000
         L     @07,CVTPTR                                          0073 00053000
         L     @11,CVTPCCAT(,@07)                                  0073 00054000
         L     R5,PCCAT00P(@15,@11)                                0073 00055000
*           IF R5->PCCAPWAV->PWAMFAFL¬='00'X/* IS MALFUNCTION ON     */ 00056000
*             THEN                                                 0074 00057000
         L     @15,PCCAPWAV(,R5)                                   0074 00058000
         CLI   PWAMFAFL(@15),X'00'                                 0074 00059000
         BE    @RF00074                                            0074 00060000
*             DO;                                                  0075 00061000
*               TS(CSDACR);         /* SET ACR ACTIVE TO TERMINATE 0076 00062000
*                                      SYSTEM                        */ 00063000
         L     @15,CVTCSD(,@07)                                    0076 00064000
         TS    CSDACR(@15)                                         0076 00065000
*               GOTO GETOUT;        /* GO CALL RTM TYPE = ACR        */ 00066000
         B     GETOUT                                              0077 00067000
*             END;                                                 0078 00068000
*         END;                                                     0079 00069000
@RF00074 DS    0H                                                  0080 00070000
*     GEN;                                                         0080 00071000
@RF00071 DS    0H                                                  0080 00072000
@RF00070 DS    0H                                                  0080 00073000
       SLL   CPUAL,1        SHIFT TO TEST NEXT CPU                      00074000
*   END;                                                           0081 00075000
         AL    CPUI,@CF00061                                       0081 00076000
         C     CPUI,@CF00110                                       0081 00077000
         BNH   @DL00069                                            0081 00078000
*GETOUT:                                                           0082 00079000
*   ;                                                              0082 00080000
GETOUT   DS    0H                                                  0083 00081000

./  ADD  SSI=40281386,NAME=IGFPTCON
         TITLE 'IGFPTCON - MCH CONSOLE WRITE ROUTINE                   *00001000
                       '                                                00002000
IGFPTCON CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IGFPTCON  74.028'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00013000
*                                                                  0047 00014000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00015000
*   /*                                                               */ 00016000
*   /* CHECK MCS PREFIX TO UCM                                       */ 00017000
*   /*                                                               */ 00018000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00019000
*                                                                  0047 00020000
*   WTOPARM=R1;                     /* SAVE INPUT PARAMETER          */ 00021000
         LR    WTOPARM,R1                                          0047 00022000
*   RFY                                                            0048 00023000
*     R1 UNRSTD;                    /* UNRESTRICT R1                 */ 00024000
*   IF UCMPRFXP=0 THEN                                             0049 00025000
         L     @07,CVTPTR                                          0049 00026000
         L     @07,UCMBASPT(,@07)                                  0049 00027000
         LR    @15,@07                                             0049 00028000
         SH    @15,@CH00143                                        0049 00029000
         ICM   @14,15,UCMPRFXP(@15)                                0049 00030000
         BZ    @RT00049                                            0049 00031000
*     RETURN;                       /* RETURN TO CALLER IF MCS PREFIX   00032000
*                                      NOT AVAILABLE                 */ 00033000
*   UCMDVEPT=UCMMCENT;              /* GET PTR TO MASTER CONSOLE UCM    00034000
*                                      ENTRY                         */ 00035000
*                                                                  0051 00036000
         L     @01,UCMMCSPT(,@15)                                  0051 00037000
         L     UCMDVEPT,UCMMCENT(,@01)                             0051 00038000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00039000
*   /*                                                               */ 00040000
*   /* ATTEMPT TO LOCATE AN ACTIVE GRAPHICS OR UNIT RECORD CONSOLE   */ 00041000
*   /*                                                               */ 00042000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00043000
*                                                                  0052 00044000
*   DO CONSCTR=(UCMVEL->UCMID)-1 BY-1 TO 0 WHILE UCMDVEPT¬=0;/*    0052 00045000
*                                      SEARCH UCM CHAIN UNTIL END OF    00046000
*                                      CHAIN REACHED OR MAXIMUM    0052 00047000
*                                      NUMBER OF CONSOLES EXAMINED 0052 00048000
*                                                            @YM06150*/ 00049000
         L     @03,CVTPTR                                          0052 00050000
         L     @03,UCMBASPT(,@03)                                  0052 00051000
         L     @03,UCMVEL(,@03)                                    0052 00052000
         SR    CONSCTR,CONSCTR                                     0052 00053000
         IC    CONSCTR,UCMID(,@03)                                 0052 00054000
         BCTR  CONSCTR,0                                           0052 00055000
         B     @DE00052                                            0052 00056000
@DL00052 SR    @03,@03                                             0052 00057000
         CR    UCMDVEPT,@03                                        0052 00058000
         BE    @DC00052                                            0052 00059000
*     IF UCMCOMPC¬=0 THEN           /* CHECK FOR COMPOSITE CONSOLE   */ 00060000
         L     @15,UCMCOMPC(,UCMDVEPT)                             0053 00061000
         CR    @15,@03                                             0053 00062000
         BE    @RF00053                                            0053 00063000
*       UCMDVEPT=UCMCOMPC;          /* GET PTR TO UCM ENTRY FOR    0054 00064000
*                                      OUTPUT DEVICE IF CONSOLE IS 0054 00065000
*                                      COMPOSITE                     */ 00066000
         LR    UCMDVEPT,@15                                        0054 00067000
*     IF UCMUF='1'B THEN            /* CHECK FOR CONSOLE ACTIVE      */ 00068000
@RF00053 TM    UCMUF(UCMDVEPT),B'00010000'                         0055 00069000
         BNO   @RF00055                                            0055 00070000
*       DO;                         /* ACTIVE CONSOLE FOUND          */ 00071000
*         IF UCMXB¬=0 THEN          /* CHECK FOR GRAPHICS DEVICE     */ 00072000
*                                                                  0057 00073000
         ICM   @03,15,UCMXB(UCMDVEPT)                              0057 00074000
         BZ    @RF00057                                            0057 00075000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00076000
*           /*                                                       */ 00077000
*           /* ACTIVE GRAPHICS CONSOLE FOUND                         */ 00078000
*           /*                                                       */ 00079000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00080000
*                                                                  0058 00081000
*           DO;                                                    0058 00082000
*             CCWCHPTR=DCMADRMS;    /* LOCATE GRAPHICS CCW CHAIN   0059 00083000
*                                                            @YM06150*/ 00084000
         L     @15,DCMTSPTR(,UCMDVEPT)                             0059 00085000
         SR    @14,@14                                             0059 00086000
         ICM   @14,7,DCMADRMS(@15)                                 0059 00087000
         LR    CCWCHPTR,@14                                        0059 00088000
*             CCWWTPTR=DCMADRMS+(DCMRMS-1)*8;/* POINT TO CCW TO BE 0060 00089000
*                                      FILLED IN BY IGFPTIOS @YM06150*/ 00090000
         SR    CCWWTPTR,CCWWTPTR                                   0060 00091000
         IC    CCWWTPTR,DCMRMS(,@15)                               0060 00092000
         BCTR  CCWWTPTR,0                                          0060 00093000
         SLA   CCWWTPTR,3                                          0060 00094000
         AR    @14,CCWWTPTR                                        0060 00095000
         LR    CCWWTPTR,@14                                        0060 00096000
*             CALL IGFPTIOS;        /* ATTEMPT TO WRITE MSG          */ 00097000
         BAL   @14,IGFPTIOS                                        0061 00098000
*             IF RETCODE=SIOGOOD THEN/* CHECK RETURN CODE            */ 00099000
         LTR   RETCODE,RETCODE                                     0062 00100000
         BZ    @RT00062                                            0062 00101000
*               GOTO CKHRDCPY;      /* ATTEMPT TO WRITE SAME MSG TO     00102000
*                                      HARDCOPY IF SIO SUCCESSFUL    */ 00103000
*           END;                    /* OTHERWISE CONTINUE CONSOLE  0064 00104000
*                                      SEARCH                        */ 00105000
*         ELSE                                                     0065 00106000
*           IF UCBTBYT3=UNITREC THEN/* CHECK FOR UNIT RECORD DEVICE  */ 00107000
*                                                                  0065 00108000
         B     @RC00057                                            0065 00109000
@RF00057 L     @03,UCBPTR(,UCMDVEPT)                               0065 00110000
         CLI   UCBTBYT3(@03),X'08'                                 0065 00111000
         BNE   @RF00065                                            0065 00112000
*             /*******************************************************/ 00113000
*             /*                                                     */ 00114000
*             /* ACTIVE UNIT RECORD CONSOLE FOUND                    */ 00115000
*             /*                                                     */ 00116000
*             /*******************************************************/ 00117000
*                                                                  0066 00118000
*             DO;                                                  0066 00119000
*               CCWCHPTR=ADDR(URECCCW);/* POINT TO UNIT RECORD CCW 0067 00120000
*                                                            @YM06150*/ 00121000
         LA    @15,URECCCW                                         0067 00122000
         LR    CCWCHPTR,@15                                        0067 00123000
*               CCWWTPTR=ADDR(URECCCW);/* POINT TO CCW TO BE FILLED     00124000
*                                      IN BY IGFPTIOS        @YM06150*/ 00125000
         LR    CCWWTPTR,@15                                        0068 00126000
*               CALL IGFPTIOS;      /* ATTEMPT TO WRITE MSG          */ 00127000
         BAL   @14,IGFPTIOS                                        0069 00128000
*               IF RETCODE=SIOGOOD THEN/* CHECK RETURN CODE          */ 00129000
         LTR   RETCODE,RETCODE                                     0070 00130000
         BZ    @RT00070                                            0070 00131000
*                 RETURN;           /* RETURN TO CALLER IF SIO     0071 00132000
*                                      SUCCESSFUL                    */ 00133000
*             END;                  /* OTHERWISE CONTINUE CONSOLE  0072 00134000
*                                      SEARCH                        */ 00135000
*       END;                                                       0073 00136000
@RF00065 DS    0H                                                  0073 00137000
@RC00057 DS    0H                                                  0074 00138000
*     UCMDVEPT=UCMALTEN;            /* GET PTR TO UCM ENTRY OF     0074 00139000
*                                      ALTERNATE                     */ 00140000
@RF00055 L     UCMDVEPT,UCMALTEN(,UCMDVEPT)                        0074 00141000
*   END;                            /* CONTINUE CONSOLE SEARCH LOOP     00142000
*                                      IF EXITING CONDITIONS NOT MET */ 00143000
*                                                                  0075 00144000
         BCTR  CONSCTR,0                                           0075 00145000
@DE00052 LTR   CONSCTR,CONSCTR                                     0075 00146000
         BNM   @DL00052                                            0075 00147000
@DC00052 DS    0H                                                  0076 00148000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00149000
*   /*                                                               */ 00150000
*   /* IF THE MESSAGE COULD NOT BE WRITTEN TO ONE OF THE CONSOLES OR */ 00151000
*   /* IF IT WAS WRITTEN TO A GRAPHICS DEVICE, AN ATTEMPT WILL BE    */ 00152000
*   /* MADE TO WRITE IT TO THE HARDCOPY DEVICE                       */ 00153000
*   /*                                                               */ 00154000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00155000
*                                                                  0076 00156000
*CKHRDCPY:                                                         0076 00157000
*   UCMDVEPT=UCMHCUCM;              /* GET PTR TO UCM ENTRY OF     0076 00158000
*                                      HARDCOPY DEVICE               */ 00159000
CKHRDCPY L     @07,CVTPTR                                          0076 00160000
         L     @07,UCMBASPT(,@07)                                  0076 00161000
         AL    @07,@CF01797                                        0076 00162000
         L     @07,UCMMCSPT(,@07)                                  0076 00163000
         L     UCMDVEPT,UCMHCUCM(,@07)                             0076 00164000
*   IF UCMSYSB='1'B                 /* CHECK FOR HARDCOPY REQUIRED   */ 00165000
*       &UCMSYSG¬='1'B              /* CHECK FOR HARDCOPY NOT SYSLOG */ 00166000
*       &UCMDVEPT¬=0                /* CHECK FOR NON-ZERO UCM ENTRY     00167000
*                                      PTR                           */ 00168000
*       &UCMUF='1'B                 /* CHECK FOR ACTIVE              */ 00169000
*       &UCBTBYT3=UNITREC THEN      /* CHECK FOR UNIT RECORD DEVICE  */ 00170000
         TM    UCMSYSB(@07),B'01000000'                            0077 00171000
         BNO   @RF00077                                            0077 00172000
         TM    UCMSYSG(@07),B'00000010'                            0077 00173000
         BNZ   @RF00077                                            0077 00174000
         LTR   UCMDVEPT,UCMDVEPT                                   0077 00175000
         BZ    @RF00077                                            0077 00176000
         TM    UCMUF(UCMDVEPT),B'00010000'                         0077 00177000
         BNO   @RF00077                                            0077 00178000
         L     @07,UCBPTR(,UCMDVEPT)                               0077 00179000
         CLI   UCBTBYT3(@07),X'08'                                 0077 00180000
         BNE   @RF00077                                            0077 00181000
*     DO;                                                          0078 00182000
*       CCWCHPTR=ADDR(URECCCW);     /* POINT TO UNIT RECORD CCW    0079 00183000
*                                                            @YM06150*/ 00184000
         LA    @07,URECCCW                                         0079 00185000
         LR    CCWCHPTR,@07                                        0079 00186000
*       CCWWTPTR=ADDR(URECCCW);     /* POINT TO CCW TO BE FILLED IN     00187000
*                                      BY IGFPTIOS           @YM06150*/ 00188000
         LR    CCWWTPTR,@07                                        0080 00189000
*       CALL IGFPTIOS;              /* ATTEMPT TO WRITE MSG TO     0081 00190000
*                                      HARDCOPY                      */ 00191000
         BAL   @14,IGFPTIOS                                        0081 00192000
*     END;                                                         0082 00193000
*   RETURN;                         /* RETURN TO CALLER              */ 00194000
@EL00001 DS    0H                                                  0083 00195000
@EF00001 DS    0H                                                  0083 00196000
@ER00001 LM    @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0083 00197000
         BR    @14                                                 0083 00198000
*                                                                  0084 00199000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00200000
*   /*                                                               */ 00201000
*   /* SUBROUTINE TO DO I/O                                          */ 00202000
*   /*                                                               */ 00203000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00204000
*                                                                  0084 00205000
*IGFPTIOS:                                                         0084 00206000
*   PROC OPTIONS(NOSAVE,NOSAVEAREA);                               0084 00207000
*                                                                  0084 00208000
IGFPTIOS DS    0H                                                  0085 00209000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00210000
*   /*                                                               */ 00211000
*   /* SAVE CURRENT I/O STATUS AND PREPARE FOR SIO                   */ 00212000
*   /*                                                               */ 00213000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00214000
*                                                                  0085 00215000
*   IONEWSAV=FLCINPSW;              /* SAVE I/O NEW PSW              */ 00216000
         MVC   IONEWSAV(8),FLCINPSW                                0085 00217000
*   IOOLDSAV=FLCIOPSW;              /* SAVE I/O OLD PSW              */ 00218000
         MVC   IOOLDSAV(8),FLCIOPSW                                0086 00219000
*   IOADSAVE=FLCIOA;                /* SAVE I/O ADDRESS              */ 00220000
         MVC   IOADSAVE(4),FLCIOA                                  0087 00221000
*   CAWSAVE=FLCCAW;                 /* SAVE CAW                      */ 00222000
         MVC   CAWSAVE(4),FLCCAW                                   0088 00223000
*   CSWSAVE=FLCCSW;                 /* SAVE CSW                      */ 00224000
         MVC   CSWSAVE(8),FLCCSW                                   0089 00225000
*   GEN REFS(CHMSKSAV,CHMSKNEW)SETS(CHMSKSAV);                     0090 00226000
         STCTL 2,2,CHMSKSAV           SAVE CURRENT CHANNEL MASKS        00227000
         LCTL  2,2,CHMSKNEW           INSURE ALL CHANNELS MASKED ON     00228000
*   FLCINPSW=MYIONPSW;              /* CHANGE I/O NEW SO THAT THIS 0091 00229000
*                                      MODULE WILL HANDLE ALL I/O  0091 00230000
*                                      INTERRUPTS                    */ 00231000
         MVC   FLCINPSW(8),MYIONPSW                                0091 00232000
*   FLCCAW=CCWCHPTR;                /* SET UP CAW WITH CCW CHAIN ADDR   00233000
*                                                            @YM06150*/ 00234000
         ST    CCWCHPTR,FLCCAW                                     0092 00235000
*   CCWDATAD=ADDR(WTOMSG);          /* SET UP 'WRITE' CCW DATA ADDR     00236000
*                                      FIELD                         */ 00237000
         LA    @04,WTOMSG(,WTOPARM)                                0093 00238000
         STCM  @04,7,CCWDATAD(CCWWTPTR)                            0093 00239000
*   CCWCOUNT=WTOLEN-(LENGTH(WTOLEN)+LENGTH(WTOJUNK));/* SET UP     0094 00240000
*                                      'WRITE' CCW BYTE COUNT FIELD  */ 00241000
         SR    @04,@04                                             0094 00242000
         ICM   @04,3,WTOLEN(WTOPARM)                               0094 00243000
         SH    @04,@CH00143                                        0094 00244000
         STH   @04,CCWCOUNT(,CCWWTPTR)                             0094 00245000
*   RETCODE=SIOGOOD;                /* INITIALIZE RETURN CODE        */ 00246000
*                                                                  0095 00247000
         SR    RETCODE,RETCODE                                     0095 00248000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00249000
*   /*                                                               */ 00250000
*   /* ATTEMPT TO WRITE MESSAGE                                      */ 00251000
*   /*                                                               */ 00252000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00253000
*                                                                  0096 00254000
*   DO SIOCTR=SIOLIMIT BY-1 TO 0;                                  0096 00255000
         L     SIOCTR,@CF01759                                     0096 00256000
@DL00096 DS    0H                                                  0097 00257000
*     SIO(UCBCHAN);                 /* ISSUE SIO AND CHECK CONDITION    00258000
*                                      CODE                          */ 00259000
         L     @04,UCBPTR(,UCMDVEPT)                               0097 00260000
         SR    @15,@15                                             0097 00261000
         ICM   @15,3,UCBCHAN(@04)                                  0097 00262000
         SIO   0(@15)                                              0097 00263000
*     BC(8,RESTORE);                /* CC=0, I/O INITIATED           */ 00264000
         BC    8,RESTORE                                           0098 00265000
*     BC(2,IGFPTINT);               /* CC=2, CHANNEL BUSY            */ 00266000
         BC    2,IGFPTINT                                          0099 00267000
*     BC(1,NOGOOD);                 /* CC=3, HARDWARE NOT OPERATIONAL*/ 00268000
*                                                                  0100 00269000
         BC    1,NOGOOD                                            0100 00270000
*/*                                    CC=1, CSW STORED              */ 00271000
*                                                                  0101 00272000
*     IF CSWCUE¬='1'B               /* CHECK FOR CONTROL UNIT END    */ 00273000
*         &CSWBUSY¬='1'B THEN       /* CHECK FOR DEVICE BUSY         */ 00274000
         TM    CSWCUE,B'00110000'                                  0101 00275000
         BZ    @RT00101                                            0101 00276000
*       GOTO NOGOOD;                /* IF NEITHER, BRANCH            */ 00277000
*IGFPTINT:                                                         0103 00278000
*     LPSW(ENABLE);                 /* ENABLE I/O INTERRUPTIONS      */ 00279000
@RF00101 DS    0H                                                  0103 00280000
IGFPTINT LPSW  ENABLE                                              0103 00281000
*ENABLNSI:                                                         0104 00282000
*     LPSW(DISABLE);                /* DISABLE I/O INTERRUPTIONS     */ 00283000
ENABLNSI LPSW  DISABLE                                             0104 00284000
*DISABNSI:                                                         0105 00285000
*   END;                            /* CONTINUE SIO LOOP IF LIMIT NOT   00286000
*                                      EXCEEDED                      */ 00287000
DISABNSI BCTR  SIOCTR,0                                            0105 00288000
         LTR   SIOCTR,SIOCTR                                       0105 00289000
         BNM   @DL00096                                            0105 00290000
*NOGOOD:                                                           0106 00291000
*   RETCODE=SIOFAIL;                /* INDICATE I/O NOT INITIATED    */ 00292000
*                                                                  0106 00293000
NOGOOD   LA    RETCODE,4                                           0106 00294000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00295000
*   /*                                                               */ 00296000
*   /* RESTORE SAVED I/O STATUS AND RETURN TO MAINLINE               */ 00297000
*   /*                                                               */ 00298000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00299000
*                                                                  0107 00300000
*RESTORE:                                                          0107 00301000
*   FLCINPSW=IONEWSAV;              /* RESTORE I/O NEW PSW           */ 00302000
RESTORE  MVC   FLCINPSW(8),IONEWSAV                                0107 00303000
*   FLCIOPSW=IOOLDSAV;              /* RESTORE I/O OLD PSW           */ 00304000
         MVC   FLCIOPSW(8),IOOLDSAV                                0108 00305000
*   FLCIOA=IOADSAVE;                /* RESTORE I/O ADDRESS           */ 00306000

*   FLCCAW=CAWSAVE;                 /* RESTORE CAW                   */ 00308000

         MVC   FLCCSW(8),CSWSAVE                                   0111 00311000
*   GEN(LCTL  2,2,CHMSKSAV)                                        0112 00312000
*   REFS(CHMSKSAV)NOSETS;           /* RESTORE CHANNEL MASKS         */ 00313000
         LCTL  2,2,CHMSKSAV                                             00314000
*   END IGFPTIOS;                   /* RETURN TO IGFPTCON MAINLINE   */ 00315000

@EF00002 DS    0H                                                  0113 00317000

./  ADD  SSI=81220419,NAME=IGFPTERM
         TITLE 'IGFPTERM - MCH PROCESSOR TERMINATION                   *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IGFPTERM CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT BALR  @15,0                                               0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL2(@EP00001-@MAINENT-2)                                 00007000
         DC    AL1(24)                                             0001 00008000
         DC    C'IGFPTERM 78122  UZ16814 '                         0001 00009000
IGFPTEFR BALR  @15,0                                               0001 00010000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00011000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00012000
         DC    AL2(@EP00120-IGFPTEFR-2)                                 00013000
         ENTRY IGFPTEFR                                                 00014000
         DROP  @15                                                      00015000
@PROLOG  BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00016000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00017000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00018000
         AH    @15,4(,@15)                                         0001 00019000
         BR    @15                                                 0001 00020000
@EP00001 DS    0H                                                  0002 00021000
*                                                                  0081 00022000
*/********************************************************************/ 00023000
*/*                                                                  */ 00024000
*/*MAINLINE-                                                         */ 00025000
*/*          IGFPTERM                                                */ 00026000
*/*                                                                  */ 00027000
*/********************************************************************/ 00028000
*                                                                  0081 00029000
*   PSAPTR=0;                       /* ADDR OF PSA IS LOC 0  @G47AN2O*/ 00030000
         SLR   PSAPTR,PSAPTR                                       0081 00031000
*   GEN( STNSM  SMBYTE,X'B8');      /* PER,I-O,EXT,DAT DISABLED      */ 00032000
          STNSM  SMBYTE,X'B8'                                           00033000
*/*********************************************************          */ 00034000
*/*  CHECK IF SYSTEM TERMINATION FROM MCH  OR ANONYMOUS CALLER       */ 00035000
*/*********************************************************          */ 00036000
*                                                                  0083 00037000
*PUTSYSDN:                                                         0083 00038000
*   ;                               /*                       @Z30LQLM*/ 00039000
PUTSYSDN DS    0H                                                  0084 00040000
*   R5=LRBPARM;                     /* SYS1.LOGREC LRB PTR           */ 00041000
         L     R5,LRBPARM(,PRMREG)                                 0084 00042000
*   IF R5->LRBHTYPE¬=LRBHMCH        /* IS THIS A ANONYMOUS CALLER    */ 00043000
*       |R5->LRBMSYST='1'B          /* OR SYSTEM TERMINATION         */ 00044000
*     THEN                                                         0085 00045000
         CLI   LRBHTYPE(R5),X'13'                                  0085 00046000
         BNE   @RT00085                                            0085 00047000
         TM    LRBMSYST(R5),B'00100000'                            0085 00048000
         BNO   @RF00085                                            0085 00049000
@RT00085 DS    0H                                                  0086 00050000
*     DO;                                                          0086 00051000
*       R4=WTOPARM;                 /* SYSTEM TERM MESSAGE PARM      */ 00052000
         L     R4,WTOPARM(,PRMREG)                                 0087 00053000
*       R2='00'X;                   /* ZERO FOR RWA TEST             */ 00054000
         SLR   @08,@08                                             0088 00055000
         LR    R2,@08                                              0088 00056000
*       R3='00'X;                   /* ZERO FOR RWA TEST             */ 00057000
         LR    R3,@08                                              0089 00058000
*       CDS(R2,R4,RWATERM);         /* IS SYSTEM TERMINATION ALREADY    00059000
*                                      IN PROGRESS ?                 */ 00060000
         L     @08,CVTPTR(,PSAPTR)                                 0090 00061000
         L     @08,RVTPTR(,@08)                                    0090 00062000
         L     @08,RWAPTR(,@08)                                    0090 00063000
         CDS   R2,R4,RWATERM(@08)                                  0090 00064000
*       BC(7,SIGIT);                /* YES. GO TO IGFPTSIG           */ 00065000
         BC    7,SIGIT                                             0091 00066000
*     END;                                                         0092 00067000
*                                                                  0093 00068000
*/*     PROCESSOR TERMINATION ROUTE                                  */ 00069000
*                                                                  0093 00070000
*   TS(PSAMCHFL);                   /* FUNCTIONAL RECOVERY SETTING   */ 00071000
@RF00085 TS    PSAMCHFL(PSAPTR)                                    0093 00072000
*   CALL IGFPSAD0;                  /* LOW ADDRESS INIT      @G51BP2O*/ 00073000
         L     @15,@CV01930                                        0094 00074000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0094 00075000
*   FLCRNPSW=RSTNPSW;               /* SET RESTART NEW PSW           */ 00076000
         MVC   FLCRNPSW(8,PSAPTR),RSTNPSW                          0095 00077000
*   FLCPNPSW=PROGNPSW;              /* PROGRAM CHECK NEM PSW         */ 00078000
         MVC   FLCPNPSW(8,PSAPTR),PROGNPSW                         0096 00079000
*   CALL IGFPSAE0;                  /* LOW ADDRESS UN-INIT   @G51BP2O*/ 00080000
         L     @15,@CV01931                                        0097 00081000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0097 00082000
*   APCCARMS='1'B;                  /* SET EMS RMS BIT               */ 00083000
         L     @15,PCCAPTR(,PSAPTR)                                0098 00084000
         L     @08,APCCARMS-3(,@15)                                0098 00085000
@GL00002 LR    @07,@08                                             0098 00086000
         O     @07,@CF02003                                        0098 00087000
         CS    @08,@07,APCCARMS-3(@15)                             0098 00088000
         BNE   @GL00002                                            0098 00089000
*   RFY                                                            0099 00090000
*     CSD BASED(CVTCSDRL);          /* REAL ADDRESS OF CDS   @YM00970*/ 00091000
*   CPUAL=CPUCPUAL;                 /* CPU ONLINE BITS IN HIGH ORDER    00092000
*                                      OF REG                        */ 00093000
         L     @08,CVTPTR(,PSAPTR)                                 0100 00094000
         L     @08,CVTCSDRL(,@08)                                  0100 00095000
         ICM   CPUAL,15,CPUCPUAL+8(@08)                            0100 00096000
*   DO I=0 TO DIM(RWAPCCAR)-1;      /* LOOP FOR EACH CPU     @G47AN2O*/ 00097000
         SLR   I,I                                                 0101 00098000
@DL00101 DS    0H                                                  0102 00099000
*     IF CPUAL<0                    /* IS CPU(I) ONLINE              */ 00100000
*       THEN                                                       0102 00101000
         SLR   @08,@08                                             0102 00102000
         CR    CPUAL,@08                                           0102 00103000
         BNL   @RF00102                                            0102 00104000
*       IF I¬=PCCACPUA              /* IS THIS THE EXECUTING CPU     */ 00105000
*         THEN                                                     0103 00106000
         L     @07,PCCAPTR(,PSAPTR)                                0103 00107000
         CH    I,PCCACPUA(,@07)                                    0103 00108000
         BE    @RF00103                                            0103 00109000
*         DO;                                                      0104 00110000
*           IF RWATERM¬=HEX0|       /* IN SYSTEM             @G47AN2O   00111000
*                                      TERMINATION           @G47AN2O*/ 00112000
*               RWAPCCAR(I+1)->     /* REAL PCCA ADDR        @G47AN2O*/ 00113000
*               PCCAPSAR->          /* REAL PSA ADDR         @G47AN2O*/ 00114000
*               PSALCCAR->          /* REAL LCCA ADDR        @G47AN2O*/ 00115000
*               LCCAVARY=OFFLINE|   /* CPU HAS ALL CHNLS     @G47AN2O   00116000
*                                      OFFLINE               @G47AN2O*/ 00117000
*               RWAPCCAR(I+1)->     /*                       @G47AN2O*/ 00118000
*               PCCAIO=HASIO|       /* CPU HAS CHNLS         @G47AN2O   00119000
*                                      ONLINE                @G47AN2O*/ 00120000
*               IOXCRHA¬=ZERO       /* CRH IS ON SYSTEM      @G47AN2O*/ 00121000
*             THEN                                                 0105 00122000
         L     @07,CVTPTR(,PSAPTR)                                 0105 00123000
         L     @15,RVTPTR(,@07)                                    0105 00124000
         L     @15,RWAPTR(,@15)                                    0105 00125000
         CLC   RWATERM(8,@15),@CB01971                             0105 00126000
         BNE   @RT00105                                            0105 00127000
         LR    @14,I                                               0105 00128000
         SLA   @14,2                                               0105 00129000
         L     @15,RWAPCCAR(@14,@15)                               0105 00130000
         L     @14,PCCAPSAR(,@15)                                  0105 00131000
         L     @14,PSALCCAR(,@14)                                  0105 00132000
         TM    LCCAVARY(@14),B'00000001'                           0105 00133000
         BO    @RT00105                                            0105 00134000
         TM    PCCAIO(@15),B'01000000'                             0105 00135000
         BO    @RT00105                                            0105 00136000
         L     @07,CVTIXAVL(,@07)                                  0105 00137000
         L     @07,IOCOMEX(,@07)                                   0105 00138000
         C     @08,IOXCRHA(,@07)                                   0105 00139000
         BE    @RF00105                                            0105 00140000
@RT00105 DS    0H                                                  0106 00141000
*             DO;                   /* SIGP HIM              @Z30LQLM*/ 00142000
*               PWACPUAD=I;         /* PHY ADDR TO SIGP      @Z30LQLM*/ 00143000
         L     @08,PCCAPTR(,PSAPTR)                                0107 00144000
         L     @08,PWAPTR(,@08)                                    0107 00145000
         STH   I,PWACPUAD(,@08)                                    0107 00146000
*               GOTO CPUFND;        /* GO SIGP PROCESSOR     @Z30LQLM*/ 00147000
         B     CPUFND                                              0108 00148000
*             END;                  /*                       @Z30LQLM*/ 00149000
*         END;                      /*                       @Z30LQLM*/ 00150000
@RF00105 DS    0H                                                  0111 00151000
*ANOCPU:                                                           0111 00152000
*     ;                                                            0111 00153000
@RF00103 DS    0H                                                  0111 00154000
@RF00102 DS    0H                                                  0111 00155000
ANOCPU   DS    0H                                                  0112 00156000
*     GEN;                                                         0112 00157000
    SLL   CPUAL,1      SHIFT TO TEST NEXT CPU                           00158000
*   END;                                                           0113 00159000
         AL    I,@CF00063                                          0113 00160000
         C     I,@CF00063                                          0113 00161000
         BNH   @DL00101                                            0113 00162000
*                                                                  0114 00163000
*/*IF WE REACH THIS POINT AND SYSTEM TERMINATION IS IN       @Z30LQLM*/ 00164000
*/*PROGRESS, RWATERM IS NON-ZERO, ALL ONLINE PROCESSORS      @Z30LQLM*/ 00165000
*/*HAVE BEEN SIGPED.  THEY WILL GO INTO THE WAIT STATE       @Z30LQLM*/ 00166000
*/*UPON FIELDING THE EXTERNAL INTERRUPT AND EXAMINING        @Z30LQLM*/ 00167000
*/*RWATERM.  IGFPTSIG HANDLES THE SIGP EMS SIGNAL FOR MCH.   @Z30LQLM*/ 00168000
*/*IF WE REACH THIS POINT AND SYSTEM TERMINATION IS NOT IN   @Z30LQLM*/ 00169000
*/*EFFECT, THERE IS NO ONLINE PROCESSOR WITH I/O CAPABILITY  @Z30LQLM*/ 00170000
*/*TO RECOVER US.  WE MUST REQUEST SYSTEM TERMINATION AND    @Z30LQLM*/ 00171000
*/*INFORM EACH ONLINE PROCESSOR TO GO INTO THE WAIT STATE.   @Z30LQLM*/ 00172000
*                                                                  0114 00173000
*   IF RWATERM='0000000000000000'X THEN/* NOT SYS TERM BUT NO      0114 00174000
*                                                            @Z30LQLM*/ 00175000
         L     @08,CVTPTR(,PSAPTR)                                 0114 00176000
         L     @08,RVTPTR(,@08)                                    0114 00177000
         L     @08,RWAPTR(,@08)                                    0114 00178000
         CLC   RWATERM(8,@08),@CB01971                             0114 00179000
         BNE   @RF00114                                            0114 00180000
*     DO;                           /* RECOVERY POSSIBLE     @Z30LQLM*/ 00181000
*       LRBPARM->LRBMSYST='1'B;     /* REQ SYS TERMINATION   @Z30LQLM*/ 00182000
         L     @08,LRBPARM(,PRMREG)                                0116 00183000
         OI    LRBMSYST(@08),B'00100000'                           0116 00184000
*       LRBPARM->LRBMWSC=PWAFRRCD+WSC;/* WAIT STATE CODE     @Z30LQLM*/ 00185000
         L     @07,PCCAPTR(,PSAPTR)                                0117 00186000
         L     @07,PWAPTR(,@07)                                    0117 00187000
         L     @07,PWAFRRCD(,@07)                                  0117 00188000
         AL    @07,WSC                                             0117 00189000
         ST    @07,LRBMWSC(,@08)                                   0117 00190000
*       GOTO PUTSYSDN;              /* INFORM CPUS OF SYSTEM TERM  0118 00191000
*                                                            @Z30LQLM*/ 00192000
         B     PUTSYSDN                                            0118 00193000
*     END;                          /*                       @Z30LQLM*/ 00194000
*IGFPTEFR:                                                         0120 00195000
*   ENTRY;                                                         0120 00196000
*                                                                  0120 00197000
@EP00120 DS    0H                                                  0120 00198000
@EC00120 DS    0H                                                  0121 00199000
*/*  THIS IS AN ENTRY POINT FOR FUNCTIONAL RECOVERY PROGRAM CHECKS   */ 00200000
*                                                                  0121 00201000
*   R4=WTOPARM;                     /* SYSTEM TERM MESSAGE PARM      */ 00202000
         L     R4,WTOPARM(,PRMREG)                                 0121 00203000
*   R5=LRBPARM;                     /* SYS1.LOGREC LRB PTR           */ 00204000
         L     R5,LRBPARM(,PRMREG)                                 0122 00205000
*   R2='00'X;                       /* ZERO FOR RWA TEST             */ 00206000
         SLR   @08,@08                                             0123 00207000
         LR    R2,@08                                              0123 00208000
*   R3='00'X;                       /* ZERO FOR RWA TEST             */ 00209000
         LR    R3,@08                                              0124 00210000
*   CDS(R2,R4,RWATERM);                                            0125 00211000
         L     @08,CVTPTR(,PSAPTR)                                 0125 00212000
         L     @08,RVTPTR(,@08)                                    0125 00213000
         L     @08,RWAPTR(,@08)                                    0125 00214000
         CDS   R2,R4,RWATERM(@08)                                  0125 00215000
*   BC(7,SIGIT);                                                   0126 00216000
         BC    7,SIGIT                                             0126 00217000
*   LRBMWSC=PWAFRRCD+WSC;           /* SET UP WAIT STATE CODE        */ 00218000
         L     @08,PCCAPTR(,PSAPTR)                                0127 00219000
         L     @07,LRBPTR(,@08)                                    0127 00220000
         L     @08,PWAPTR(,@08)                                    0127 00221000
         L     @08,PWAFRRCD(,@08)                                  0127 00222000
         AL    @08,WSC                                             0127 00223000
         ST    @08,LRBMWSC(,@07)                                   0127 00224000
*   LRBMSYST='1'B;                  /* SET SYSTEM TERMINATION BIT IN    00225000
*                                      LRB                           */ 00226000
         OI    LRBMSYST(@07),B'00100000'                           0128 00227000
*   GO TO SIGIT;                    /* GO TO IGFPTSIG                */ 00228000
         B     SIGIT                                               0129 00229000
*CPUFND:                                                           0130 00230000
*   ;                                                              0130 00231000
*                                                                  0130 00232000
CPUFND   DS    0H                                                  0131 00233000
*/*WE NOW FOUND A NON-EXECUTING ONLINE CPU AND ARE READY TO SIGP EMS */ 00234000
*                                                                  0131 00235000
*   DO SIGDEX=1 TO SIGBUSY;         /* SIGP COUNT             @YM6877*/ 00236000
         LA    SIGDEX,1                                            0131 00237000
@DL00131 DS    0H                                                  0132 00238000
*     GEN(  SIGP   R6,R3,X'03');    /* SIGP EMERGENCY SIGNAL         */ 00239000
           SIGP   R6,R3,X'03'                                           00240000
*     BC(8,PROCEED);                /* FOUND A CPU GO TEST ABILITY TO   00241000
*                                      HANDLE                        */ 00242000
         BC    8,PROCEED                                           0133 00243000
*   END;                                                           0134 00244000
         AL    SIGDEX,@CF00063                                     0134 00245000
         C     SIGDEX,@CF01958                                     0134 00246000
         BNH   @DL00131                                            0134 00247000
*   GOTO ANOCPU;                    /* GO GET ANOTHER CPU TO SIGP    */ 00248000
         B     ANOCPU                                              0135 00249000
*PROCEED:                                                          0136 00250000
*   ;                                                              0136 00251000
PROCEED  DS    0H                                                  0137 00252000
*   IF RWATERM¬='0000000000000000'X THEN                           0137 00253000
         L     @08,CVTPTR(,PSAPTR)                                 0137 00254000
         L     @08,RVTPTR(,@08)                                    0137 00255000
         L     @08,RWAPTR(,@08)                                    0137 00256000
         CLC   RWATERM(8,@08),@CB01971                             0137 00257000
         BNE   @RT00137                                            0137 00258000
*     GOTO ANOCPU;                  /* GO GET ANOTHER CPU TO SIGP    */ 00259000
*EMSLP:                                                            0139 00260000
*   ;                                                              0139 00261000
EMSLP    DS    0H                                                  0140 00262000
*   IF PCCARMS='0'B                 /* IS THE EMS BIT TURNED OFF     */ 00263000
*     THEN                                                         0140 00264000
         L     @08,PCCAPTR(,PSAPTR)                                0140 00265000
         TM    PCCARMS(@08),B'00000001'                            0140 00266000
         BNZ   @RF00140                                            0140 00267000
*     DO;                           /*                       @YM34506*/ 00268000
*       CALL IGFPSAD0;              /* LOW ADDRESS INIT      @G51BP2O*/ 00269000
         L     @15,@CV01930                                        0142 00270000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0142 00271000
*       FLCPNPSW=VSTOPPSW;          /* LOAD PROGRAM NEW PSW IN CASE     00272000
*                                      IEEVSTOP GETS IN TROBLE     0143 00273000
*                                                            @YM34506*/ 00274000
         MVC   FLCPNPSW(8,PSAPTR),VSTOPPSW                         0143 00275000
*       FLCMNPSW=VSTOPPSW;          /* LOAD MACHINE NEW PSW IN CASE     00276000
*                                      IEEVSTOP GETS IN TROBLE     0144 00277000
*                                                            @YM34506*/ 00278000
         MVC   FLCMNPSW(8,PSAPTR),VSTOPPSW                         0144 00279000
*       CALL IGFPSAE0;              /* LOW ADDRESS UN-INIT   @G51BP2O*/ 00280000
         L     @15,@CV01931                                        0145 00281000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0145 00282000
*       CALL IEEVSTOP;              /* ONE WAY CALL          @YM34506*/ 00283000
         L     @15,@CV01966                                        0146 00284000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0146 00285000
*     END;                                                         0147 00286000
*   R5=RWAPCCAR(I+1);               /* GET READY TO CHECK SIGNALED 0148 00287000
*                                      CPU                   @YM00964*/ 00288000
@RF00140 LR    @08,I                                               0148 00289000
         SLA   @08,2                                               0148 00290000
         L     @07,CVTPTR(,PSAPTR)                                 0148 00291000
         L     @07,RVTPTR(,@07)                                    0148 00292000
         L     @07,RWAPTR(,@07)                                    0148 00293000
         L     R5,RWAPCCAR(@08,@07)                                0148 00294000
*   IF R5->PCCARMS='1'B THEN                                       0149 00295000
         TM    PCCARMS(R5),B'00000001'                             0149 00296000
         BO    @RT00149                                            0149 00297000
*     GOTO ANOCPU;                  /* GET ANOTHER CPU TO SIGP       */ 00298000
*   GEN(   SIGP   R6,R3,X'01');     /* SIGP SENSE                    */ 00299000
            SIGP   R6,R3,X'01'                                          00300000
*   BC(4,CKSTOP);                   /* CHECK RETURN SENSE FOR CHECK     00301000
*                                      STOP                          */ 00302000
         BC    4,CKSTOP                                            0152 00303000
*SYSTERM:                                                          0153 00304000
*   ;                                                              0153 00305000
*                                                                  0153 00306000
SYSTERM  DS    0H                                                  0154 00307000
*/*    CHECK TO SEE IF SYSTEM TERMINATION IS IN PROGRESS             */ 00308000
*                                                                  0154 00309000
*   IF RWATERM¬='0000000000000000'X THEN                           0154 00310000
         L     @08,CVTPTR(,PSAPTR)                                 0154 00311000
         L     @08,RVTPTR(,@08)                                    0154 00312000
         L     @07,RWAPTR(,@08)                                    0154 00313000
         CLC   RWATERM(8,@07),@CB01971                             0154 00314000
         BE    @RF00154                                            0154 00315000
*     CALL RVTTSIG;                 /* ONE WAY CALL                  */ 00316000
         L     @15,RVTPTSIG(,@08)                                  0155 00317000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0155 00318000
*   ELSE                                                           0156 00319000
*     GOTO EMSLP;                   /* CHECK EMS BIT AGAIN           */ 00320000
*CKSTOP:                                                           0157 00321000
*   ;                                                              0157 00322000
*                                                                  0157 00323000
CKSTOP   DS    0H                                                  0158 00324000
*/*   AFTER SIGP SENSE CHECK TO SEE IF CPU IS IN CHECK STOP STATE    */ 00325000
*/*   IF SO GO AND GET ANOTHER CPU AND SIGP AGAIN                    */ 00326000
*                                                                  0158 00327000
*   CKSTREG='00000010'X;            /* CHECK STOP BIT IN SIGP RETURN */ 00328000
         LA    CKSTREG,16                                          0158 00329000
*   IF(CKSTREG&R6)='00'X            /* WAS CHECK STOP BIT ON IN    0159 00330000
*                                      RETURN                        */ 00331000
*     THEN                                                         0159 00332000
         LR    @08,CKSTREG                                         0159 00333000
         NR    @08,R6                                              0159 00334000
         LTR   @08,@08                                             0159 00335000
         BZ    @RT00159                                            0159 00336000
*     GOTO SYSTERM;                 /* CHECK SYSTEM TERMINATION      */ 00337000
*   ELSE                                                           0161 00338000
*     GOTO ANOCPU;                  /* GO GET ANOTHER CPU TO SIGP    */ 00339000
         B     ANOCPU                                              0161 00340000
*SIGIT:                                                            0162 00341000
*   CALL RVTTSIG;                   /* ONE WAY CALL                  */ 00342000
SIGIT    L     @08,CVTPTR(,PSAPTR)                                 0162 00343000
         L     @08,RVTPTR(,@08)                                    0162 00344000
         L     @15,RVTPTSIG(,@08)                                  0162 00345000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0162 00346000
*PSWRSTRT:                                                         0163 00347000
*   ;                                                              0163 00348000
PSWRSTRT DS    0H                                                  0164 00349000
*   GEN REFS(FLCROPSW);                                            0164 00350000
  LPSW     FLCROPSW                                                     00351000
*   END IGFPTERM                                                   0165 00352000
*                                                                  0165 00353000
