./  ADD  SSI=73130185,NAME=IGFTMCHK
         TITLE 'IGFTMCHK- MVS MISSING INTERRUPT HANDLER                *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IGFTMCHK CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IGFTMCHK  77.313'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @08,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@08                                         0001 00013000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0001 00014000
         GETMAIN  R,LV=(0)                                              00015000
         LR    @09,@01                                             0001 00016000
         USING @DATD,@09                                           0001 00017000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                      0001 00018000
         LM    @00,@01,20(@13)                                     0001 00019000
         ST    @09,8(,@13)                                         0001 00020000
         LR    @13,@09                                             0001 00021000
RBPRFXLN EQU 64                                                         00022000
RBPRFLNA EQU 32                                                         00023000
PRBLEN   EQU 136                                                        00024000
SIRBLEN  EQU 200                                                        00025000
TIRBLEN  EQU 136                                                        00026000
IRBLEN   EQU 128                                                        00027000
SVRBLEN  EQU 224                                                        00028000
*                                                                  0198 00029000
*/********************************************************************/ 00030000
*/*                                                                  */ 00031000
*/*  INITIALIZATION: IGFTMCHK INITIALIZATION ROUTINE                 */ 00032000
*/*                                                                  */ 00033000
*/*  INPUT: NONE                                                     */ 00034000
*/*                                                                  */ 00035000
*/*  FUNCTION:                                                       */ 00036000
*/*           1.OBTAIN SQA FOR BUILDING TQE,DDRCOM,ECB AND SRB       */ 00037000
*/*             FOR SCHEDULE IGFTMC01                                */ 00038000
*/*           2.ISSUE ESTAE FOR ABNORMAL TERMINATION                 */ 00039000
*/*           3.INITIALIZE DDRCOM                                    */ 00040000
*/*           4.WRITE IPL RECORD TO SYS1.LOGREC                      */ 00041000
*/*                                                                  */ 00042000
*/*  OUTPUT: WORK AREA FOR TQE, DDRCOM,ECB AND SRB ARE OBTAINED      */ 00043000
*/*          IPL RECORD ARE WRITTEN TO SYS1.LOGREC                   */ 00044000
*/*          ESTABLISH ESTAE EXIT ROUTINE TO HANDLE ABNORMAL         */ 00045000
*/*          TERMINATION                                             */ 00046000
*/*                                                                  */ 00047000
*/*                                                                  */ 00048000
*/********************************************************************/ 00049000
*                                                                  0198 00050000
*   TQELEN=(LENGTH(TQE)+SEVEN)/EIGHT*EIGHT;/* ROUND TQE TO DOUBLE  0198 00051000
*                                      WORD                          */ 00052000
         LA    TQELEN,128                                          0198 00053000
*   DDRCMLEN=(LENGTH(DDRCOMWK)+SEVEN)/EIGHT*EIGHT;/* SETUP TOTAL   0199 00054000
*                                      DDRCOM AND MIH LOCAL WORK AREA*/ 00055000
         LA    @12,224                                             0199 00056000
         ST    @12,DDRCMLEN                                        0199 00057000
*   SRBLEN=(LENGTH(SRB)+SEVEN)/EIGHT*EIGHT;/* ROUND SRB TO DOUBLE  0200 00058000
*                                      WORD                          */ 00059000
         LA    SRBLEN,48                                           0200 00060000
*   SQASIZE=TQELEN+SRBLEN+DDRCMLEN+LENGTH(ECB)+LENGTH(PARMLIST);/* 0201 00061000
*                                      SET UP FOR GETMAIN            */ 00062000
         LR    @03,TQELEN                                          0201 00063000
         ALR   @03,SRBLEN                                          0201 00064000
         ALR   @03,@12                                             0201 00065000
         AL    @03,@CF00790                                        0201 00066000
         ST    @03,SQASIZE                                         0201 00067000
*   RFY                                                            0202 00068000
*     RTNCODE RSTD;                 /* RESTRICT REG 15               */ 00069000
*   DO;                             /* GETMAIN (RC) LV(SQASIZE)    0203 00070000
*                                      SP(245)                       */ 00071000
*     RESPECIFY                                                    0204 00072000
*      (GPR01F,                                                    0204 00073000
*       GPR15F,                                                    0204 00074000
*       GPR00F) RESTRICTED;                                        0204 00075000
*     GPR01F=0;                     /* REG 1 MUST BE ZERO            */ 00076000
         SLR   GPR01F,GPR01F                                       0205 00077000
*     GPR15F=0;                     /* RC-TYPE GETMAIN               */ 00078000
         SLR   GPR15F,GPR15F                                       0206 00079000
*     GPR00F=SQASIZE;               /* LENGTH REQUESTED              */ 00080000
         LR    GPR00F,@03                                          0207 00081000
*     GPR15F=GPR15F|((245)*256);    /* SP IN BYTE 2                  */ 00082000
         O     GPR15F,@CF02958                                     0208 00083000
*     SVC(120);                     /* RC/RU-FORM OF GETMAIN         */ 00084000
         SVC   120                                                 0209 00085000
*     RESPECIFY                                                    0210 00086000
*      (GPR01F,                                                    0210 00087000
*       GPR15F,                                                    0210 00088000
*       GPR00F) UNRESTRICTED;                                      0210 00089000
*   END;                            /* GETMAIN (RC) LV(SQASIZE)    0211 00090000
*                                      SP(245)                       */ 00091000
*   RFY                                                            0212 00092000
*    (R0,                                                          0212 00093000
*     R1) RSTD;                     /* RESTRICT REG 0,1              */ 00094000
*   IF RTNCODE¬=ZERO THEN           /* GETMAIN SUCCESSFUL?           */ 00095000
         LTR   RTNCODE,RTNCODE                                     0213 00096000
         BNZ   @RT00213                                            0213 00097000
*     GOTO MIHEXIT;                 /* TERMINATE MIH FOR GETMAIN   0214 00098000
*                                      FAILS                         */ 00099000
*   TQEPTR=R1;                      /* GET PTR FOR TQE               */ 00100000
         ST    R1,TQEPTR                                           0215 00101000
*   SRBPTR=TQEPTR+TQELEN;           /* GET PTR FOR SRB               */ 00102000
         L     @14,TQEPTR                                          0216 00103000
         ALR   @14,TQELEN                                          0216 00104000
         LR    SRBPTR,@14                                          0216 00105000
*   DDRPTR=SRBPTR+SRBLEN;           /* SET UP PTR FOR DDRCOM         */ 00106000
         LR    DDRPTR,SRBPTR                                       0217 00107000
         ALR   DDRPTR,SRBLEN                                       0217 00108000
*   ECBPTR=DDRPTR+DDRCMLEN;         /* GET PTR FOR ECB               */ 00109000
         LR    @14,DDRPTR                                          0218 00110000
         AL    @14,DDRCMLEN                                        0218 00111000
         ST    @14,ECBPTR                                          0218 00112000
*   PARMPTR=ECBPTR+LENGTH(ECB);     /* GET PTR TO PARM LIST          */ 00113000
         AL    @14,@CF00041                                        0219 00114000
         ST    @14,PARMPTR                                         0219 00115000
*   R0=R1;                          /* GET GETMAIN ADDRESS           */ 00116000
         LR    R0,R1                                               0220 00117000
*   RFY                                                            0221 00118000
*     R14 RSTD;                     /* RESTRICT REG 14               */ 00119000
*   R1=SQASIZE;                     /* GET GETMAIN LENGTH            */ 00120000
         L     R1,SQASIZE                                          0222 00121000
*   MVCL(R0,R14);                   /* CLEAR GETMAIN AREA ZERO MVCL     00122000
*                                      BASED ON REG 15 ZERO          */ 00123000
         MVCL  R0,R14                                              0223 00124000
*   RFY                                                            0224 00125000
*    (R0,                                                          0224 00126000
*     R1,                                                          0224 00127000
*     R14,                                                         0224 00128000
*     RTNCODE) UNRSTD;              /* RELEASE REG 0,1,14,15         */ 00129000
*   DO;                             /* ?IGFDERR INIT                 */ 00130000
*                                                                  0225 00131000
*     /***************************************************************/ 00132000
*     /*                                                             */ 00133000
*     /* IGFDERR - INITIALIZE RECOVERY ENVIRONMENT                   */ 00134000
*     /*                                                             */ 00135000
*     /***************************************************************/ 00136000
*                                                                  0226 00137000
*     DERPLIST=DERPLIST&&DERPLIST;  /* CLEAR PARAMETER LIST          */ 00138000
         XC    DERPLIST(48),DERPLIST                               0226 00139000
*     DERFUNK=DERINIT;              /* INDICATE INIT FUNCTION        */ 00140000
         MVI   DERFUNK,X'01'                                       0227 00141000

         LA    @12,DERRECPM                                        0228 00143000

         LA    @12,IGFTMCHS                                        0229 00146000
         ST    @12,DERSPEC                                         0229 00147000
*     DERRETRY=ADDR(IGFTMCHR);      /* POINT TO RETRY ROUTINE        */ 00148000
         LA    @12,IGFTMCHR                                        0230 00149000
         ST    @12,DERRETRY                                        0230 00150000
*     GEN SETS(DERDATD)(MVC DERDATD,@SIZDATD);/* SET UP SPN, SIZE    */ 00151000
         MVC DERDATD,@SIZDATD                                           00152000
*     DERPFX=DERRMASK;              /* SET UP RUB MASK               */ 00153000
         MVC   DERPFX(2),@CB02791                                  0232 00154000
*     DERRCODE=CODEBASE;            /* SAVE CODEREG                  */ 00155000
         ST    CODEBASE,DERRCODE                                   0233 00156000

         ST    DATABASE,DERRDATA                                   0234 00158000

         ST    DDRPTR,DERRDDR                                      0235 00160000
*     DERRSAVE=SAVEPTR;             /* SAVE REGISTER 13              */ 00161000
         ST    SAVEPTR,DERRSAVE                                    0236 00162000
*     CALL IGFDE0(DERPLIST);        /* ISSUE ESTAE                   */ 00163000
         LA    @12,DERPLIST                                        0237 00164000
         ST    @12,@AL00001                                        0237 00165000
         L     @15,@CV02814                                        0237 00166000
         LA    @01,@AL00001                                        0237 00167000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0237 00168000
*   END;                            /* ?IGFDERR INIT ESTABLISH ESTAE */ 00169000
*   DDRUTCB=TMCTCBP;                /* GET PTR TO MIH TCB            */ 00170000
         L     @12,CVTPTR                                          0239 00171000

         L     @12,TMCTCBP+4(,@12)                                 0239 00173000
         ST    @12,DDRUTCB(,DDRPTR)                                0239 00174000
*   DERPTR=ADDR(DERPLIST);          /* GET ADDR OF DERPLIST          */ 00175000
         LA    DERPTR,DERPLIST                                     0240 00176000
*   DDRREC1=DDRRIPL;                /* INDICATE TO WRITE IPL REC     */ 00177000
         MVI   DDRREC1(DDRPTR),X'04'                               0241 00178000
*   CALL IGFDR0;                    /* CALL DDR RECORDER             */ 00179000
         L     @15,@CV02812                                        0242 00180000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0242 00181000
*   DDRPTR=DERRDDR;                 /* RESET DDRCOM PTR              */ 00182000
         L     DDRPTR,DERRDDR                                      0243 00183000
*                                                                  0244 00184000
*/********************************************************************/ 00185000
*/*                                                                  */ 00186000
*/*  SET MIH TIME INTERVAL: SET USER PROVIDED TIME INTERVAL          */ 00187000
*/*                                                                  */ 00188000
*/*  INPUT: DDRPTR- PTR TO DDRCOM                                    */ 00189000
*/*                                                                  */ 00190000
*/*  FUNCTION: CHECK TO SEE IF THE USER PROVIDED TIME IS A VALID     */ 00191000
*/*            ONE. IF SO, MOVE IT INTO THE DDRCOM TO BE USED        */ 00192000
*/*            BY SETDIE. IF INVALID,SET TIME INTERVAL AS 3 MINUTES  */ 00193000
*/*            FOR DEVICES OTHER THAN MSS.THE TIME INTERVAL FOR MSS  */ 00194000
*/*            WILL BE 4 TIMES(USER MAY ALSO DEFINE) OVER THE REGULAR*/ 00195000
*/*            TIME INTERVAL. IN THIS CASE IT WILL BE 12 MINUTES     */ 00196000
*/*                                                                  */ 00197000
*/*                                                                  */ 00198000
*/*  OUTPUT:   DDRMIHTD- MIH TIME INTERVAL IN HHMMSSTH               */ 00199000
*/*            MIHSECND- MIH TIME INTERVAL IN SECONDS                */ 00200000
*/*                      THE HUNDREDTH OF SECONDS ARE IGNORED        */ 00201000
*/*            MSSCOUNT- 3330V MSS TIME LIMIT COUNTER                */ 00202000
*/*            MIHINTVL- COPY OF IGFINTVL FOR EXIT ROUTINES  @G24LNLC*/ 00203000
*/*                                                                  */ 00204000
*/*                                                                  */ 00205000
*/********************************************************************/ 00206000
*                                                                  0244 00207000
*   DO I=ONE TO LENGTH(INTVL) WHILE(TIMERR=OFF);/* CHECK USER TIME   */ 00208000
         LA    I,1                                                 0244 00209000
@DL00244 TM    TIMERR(DDRPTR),B'10000000'                          0244 00210000
         BNZ   @DC00244                                            0244 00211000
*     IF INTVL(I)<ZERODIG|INTVL(I)>NINE THEN/* VALUE IS 0-9 ?        */ 00212000
         L     @12,@CV02815                                        0245 00213000
         ALR   @12,I                                               0245 00214000
         BCTR  @12,0                                               0245 00215000
         CLI   INTVL(@12),C'0'                                     0245 00216000
         BL    @RT00245                                            0245 00217000
         L     @12,@CV02815                                        0245 00218000
         ALR   @12,I                                               0245 00219000
         BCTR  @12,0                                               0245 00220000
         CLI   INTVL(@12),C'9'                                     0245 00221000
         BNH   @RF00245                                            0245 00222000
@RT00245 DS    0H                                                  0246 00223000
*       TIMERR=ON;                  /* NO-SET TIME ERROR             */ 00224000
         OI    TIMERR(DDRPTR),B'10000000'                          0246 00225000
*   END;                            /* END OF SCAN SPECIFIED USER  0247 00226000
*                                      TIME INTERVAL                 */ 00227000
@RF00245 AL    I,@CF00047                                          0247 00228000
         C     I,@CF00074                                          0247 00229000
         BNH   @DL00244                                            0247 00230000
@DC00244 DS    0H                                                  0248 00231000
*   IF TIMERR=OFF&INTVL¬=DZERO THEN /* ALL CHARACTERS VALID?         */ 00232000
         TM    TIMERR(DDRPTR),B'10000000'                          0248 00233000
         BNZ   @RF00248                                            0248 00234000
         L     @12,@CV02815                                        0248 00235000
         CLC   INTVL(8,@12),@CC02842                               0248 00236000
         BE    @RF00248                                            0248 00237000
*     DDRMIHT=INTVL;                /* YES-SET USER SPECIFIED TIME   */ 00238000
         L     @12,@CV02815                                        0249 00239000
         MVC   DDRMIHT(8,DDRPTR),INTVL(@12)                        0249 00240000
*   ELSE                            /* NO                            */ 00241000
*     DDRMIHT=TMCTIME;              /* SET DEFAULT TIME-3 MINUTES    */ 00242000
         B     @RC00248                                            0250 00243000
@RF00248 MVC   DDRMIHT(8,DDRPTR),@CC02828                          0250 00244000
*   PACK(MIHOUR,TMCHR);             /* PACK HOUR TO DECIMAL          */ 00245000
@RC00248 PACK  MIHOUR(2),TMCHR(2,DDRPTR)                           0251 00246000
*   CVB(HR,MIHOUR);                 /* CONVERT HOUR TO BINARY        */ 00247000
         XC    @TS00001(8),@TS00001                                0252 00248000
         MVC   @TS00001+6(2),MIHOUR                                0252 00249000
         CVB   @12,@TS00001                                        0252 00250000
         ST    @12,HR                                              0252 00251000
*   PACK(MIHMIM,TMCMM);             /* PACK MINUTES TO DECIMAL       */ 00252000
         PACK  MIHMIM(2),TMCMM(2,DDRPTR)                           0253 00253000
*   CVB(MM,MIHMIM);                 /* CONVERT MINUTES TO BINARY     */ 00254000
         XC    @TS00001(8),@TS00001                                0254 00255000
         MVC   @TS00001+6(2),MIHMIM                                0254 00256000
         CVB   @11,@TS00001                                        0254 00257000
         ST    @11,MM                                              0254 00258000
*   PACK(MIHSEC,TMCSS);             /* PACK SECONDES TO DECIMAL      */ 00259000
         PACK  MIHSEC(2),TMCSS(2,DDRPTR)                           0255 00260000
*   CVB(SS,MIHSEC);                 /* CONVERT SECONDS TO BINARY     */ 00261000
         XC    @TS00001(8),@TS00001                                0256 00262000
         MVC   @TS00001+6(2),MIHSEC                                0256 00263000
         CVB   @06,@TS00001                                        0256 00264000
         ST    @06,SS                                              0256 00265000
*   MIHSECND=(HR*SIXTY+MM)*SIXTY+SS;/* STORE TIME INTERVAL IN SECONDS*/ 00266000
         LA    @05,60                                              0257 00267000
         LR    @01,@12                                             0257 00268000
         MR    @00,@05                                             0257 00269000
         ALR   @01,@11                                             0257 00270000
         MR    @00,@05                                             0257 00271000
         ALR   @01,@06                                             0257 00272000
         ST    @01,MIHSECND(,DDRPTR)                               0257 00273000
*   MIHINTVL=INDATA;                /* COPY INTVL INTO WORKAREA FOR     00274000
*                                      USE BY EXITS          @G24LNLC*/ 00275000
         L     @12,@CV02815                                        0258 00276000
         MVC   MIHINTVL(12,DDRPTR),INDATA(@12)                     0258 00277000
*   MIHINTVL(1:8)=DDRMIHT;          /* PUT IN CORRECTED TIME INTERVAL   00278000
*                                      IN CASE OF INPUT ERROR      0259 00279000
*                                                            @G24LNLC*/ 00280000
         MVC   MIHINTVL(8,DDRPTR),DDRMIHT(DDRPTR)                  0259 00281000
*   MIHINTVA=ADDR(MIHINTVL);        /* SET UP FOR EXITS      @G24LNLC*/ 00282000
         LA    @12,MIHINTVL(,DDRPTR)                               0260 00283000
         ST    @12,MIHINTVA(,DDRPTR)                               0260 00284000
*                                                                  0261 00285000
*/********************************************************************/ 00286000
*/*                                                                  */ 00287000
*/*  INIT CONTROL BLOCKS: TQE AND SRB WILL BE INTILIZED              */ 00288000
*/*                                                                  */ 00289000
*/*  INPUT: TQEPTR WILL POINT TO TQE                                 */ 00290000
*/*         SRBPTR WILL POINT TO SRB                                 */ 00291000
*/*                                                                  */ 00292000
*/*  FUNCTION:TQE AND SRB WILL BE INITIALIZED TO CALL SETDIE         */ 00293000
*/*           TO  SCHEDULE A SRB FOR CHECKING UCBS(IGFTMC01)         */ 00294000
*/*           MIH WILL BE TERMINATED IF SETDIE FAILS                 */ 00295000
*/*                                                                  */ 00296000
*/*  OUTPUT: TQE AND SRB ARE INITIALIZED                             */ 00297000
*/*                                                                  */ 00298000
*/********************************************************************/ 00299000
*/********************************************************************/ 00300000
*/*                                                                  */ 00301000
*/*  INITIALIZE SRB FOR CHECK UCB LIST IN THE SYSTEM                 */ 00302000
*/*  THE SRB HAS NO RELATIONSHIP WITH THE TCB                        */ 00303000
*/*                                                                  */ 00304000
*/********************************************************************/ 00305000
*                                                                  0261 00306000
*   SRBID=CSRBID;                   /* SET SRB ID                    */ 00307000

*/*                                                                  */ 00332000
*/*  IGFTMC01 (IN MODULE IGFTMC00) IS SCHEDULED AS AN SRB TO PERFORM */ 00333000
*/*  INITIALIZATION OF EXIT ROUTINE TABLES.  SUSPEND AND CALLDISP    */ 00334000
*/*  ARE USED TO CAUSE SERIALIZATION OF THE SRB.  IT WILL ISSUE      */ 00335000

*       GPR15F,                                                    0364 00686000
*       GPR00F) RESTRICTED;                                        0364 00687000
*     GPR01F=0;                     /* REG 1 MUST BE ZERO            */ 00688000
         SLR   GPR01F,GPR01F                                       0365 00689000
*     GPR15F=1;                     /* SET TYPE                      */ 00690000
         LA    GPR15F,1                                            0366 00691000
*     GPR00F=LENGTH(MSGBLK);        /* LENGTH REQUESTED              */ 00692000
         LA    GPR00F,16                                           0367 00693000
*     GPR01F=ADDR(MSGBLK);          /* SET REGISTER ONE              */ 00694000
         LR    GPR01F,MSGPTR                                       0368 00695000
*     GPR15F=GPR15F+((245)*256);    /* SUBPOOL VALUE                 */ 00696000
         AL    GPR15F,@CF02958                                     0369 00697000
*     SVC(120);                     /* RC/RU-FORM OF GETMAIN         */ 00698000
         SVC   120                                                 0370 00699000
*     RESPECIFY                                                    0371 00700000
*      (GPR01F,                                                    0371 00701000
*       GPR15F,                                                    0371 00702000
*       GPR00F) UNRESTRICTED;                                      0371 00703000
*   END;                            /* FREEMAIN(RC)                0372 00704000
*                                      LV(LENGTH(MSGBLK))A(MSGBLK) 0372 00705000
*                                      SP(245)                       */ 00706000
*   GOTO MSGDEQ;                                                   0373 00707000
         B     MSGDEQ                                              0373 00708000
*IGFTMCHR:                                                         0374 00709000
*   DO;                             /* ?IGFDERR CANCEL               */ 00710000
*                                                                  0374 00711000
IGFTMCHR DS    0H                                                  0375 00712000
*     /***************************************************************/ 00713000
*     /*                                                             */ 00714000
*     /* IGFDERR - CANCEL RECOVERY ENVIRONMENT                       */ 00715000
*     /*                                                             */ 00716000
*     /***************************************************************/ 00717000
*                                                                  0375 00718000
*     DERFUNK=DERCANC;              /* INDICATE CANCEL               */ 00719000
         MVI   DERFUNK,X'02'                                       0375 00720000
*     CALL IGFDE0(DERPLIST);        /* CANCEL ESTAE                  */ 00721000
         LA    @14,DERPLIST                                        0376 00722000
         ST    @14,@AL00001                                        0376 00723000
         L     @15,@CV02814                                        0376 00724000
         LA    @01,@AL00001                                        0376 00725000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0376 00726000
*   END;                            /* ?IGFDERR CANCEL CANCEL ESTAE     00727000
*                                      FOR IGFTMCHK                  */ 00728000
*MIHEXIT:                                                          0378 00729000
*   RETURN;                         /* RETURN TO DISPATCHER          */ 00730000
@EL00001 L     @13,4(,@13)                                         0378 00731000
@EF00001 L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0378 00732000
         LR    @01,@09                                             0378 00733000
         FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1)                                        00734000
@ER00001 LM    @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0378 00735000
         BR    @14                                                 0378 00736000
*                                                                  0379 00737000
*/********************************************************************/ 00738000
*/*                                                                  */ 00739000
*/*  SOUBROUTINE: IGFTMCHS                                           */ 00740000
*/*                                                                  */ 00741000
*/*  DESCRIPTIVE-NAME: IGFTMCK ESTAE EXIT ROUTINE                    */ 00742000
*/*                                                                  */ 00743000
*/*  FUNCTION: IGFTMCHS IS ENTERED AS A SUBROUTINE OF IGFDE0.ITS     */ 00744000
*/*            PURPOSE IS TO DETERMINE WHEN MIH REQUIRES RETRY.      */ 00745000
*/*            WHEN THE ERROR OCCURRED IN MIH MAINLINE THE MIH       */ 00746000
*/*            TASK WILL BE TERMINATED. IF THE ERROR OCCURED IN      */ 00747000
*/*            ISSUING MIH MESSAGES,THEN THE MESSAGE PROCESSING      */ 00748000
*/*            WILL BE RETRIED THREE TIME BEFORE TERMINATION         */ 00749000
*/*                                                                  */ 00750000
*/*  NOTES: NONE                                                     */ 00751000
*/*                                                                  */ 00752000
*/*    DEPENDCIES: NONE                                              */ 00753000
*/*                                                                  */ 00754000
*/*    REGISTERS-CONVENTIONS: SDWAPTR(REG0)-PTR TO SDWA              */ 00755000
*/*                           SEE MODLUE SPECIFICATION               */ 00756000
*/*                                                                  */ 00757000
*/*  ENTRY-POINT: IGFTMEST                                           */ 00758000
*/*                                                                  */ 00759000
*/*    PURPOSE: TO HANDLE IGFTMCHK ABNORMAL TERMINATION              */ 00760000
*/*                                                                  */ 00761000
*/*    LINKAGE:CALL                                                  */ 00762000
*/*                                                                  */ 00763000
*/*    INPUT: SDWAPTR(REG 0) -PTR TO SDWA OR ZERO                    */ 00764000
*/*                                                                  */ 00765000
*/*    OUTPUT: NONE                                                  */ 00766000
*/*                                                                  */ 00767000
*/*    EXIT-NORMAL: IGFTMCHW-MIH RETRY ENTRY POINT                   */ 00768000
*/*                                                                  */ 00769000
*/*                                                                  */ 00770000
*/*    EXIT-ERROR:  NONE                                             */ 00771000
*/*                                                                  */ 00772000
*/*  EXTERNAL-REFERENCES:                                            */ 00773000
*/*    DATA-AREA: SDWA                                               */ 00774000
*/*                                                                  */ 00775000
*/********************************************************************/ 00776000
*                                                                  0379 00777000
*IGFTMCHS:                                                         0379 00778000
*   PROC OPTIONS(NOSAVE,NOSAVEAREA);                               0379 00779000
         B     @EL00001                                            0379 00780000
IGFTMCHS DS    0H                                                  0380 00781000
*   RFY                                                            0380 00782000
*     SDWAREG RSTD;                 /* RESTRICT REG 0                */ 00783000
*   SDWAPTR=SDWAREG;                /* SET SDWAPTR                   */ 00784000
         LR    SDWAPTR,SDWAREG                                     0381 00785000
*   IF SDWAPTR¬=ZERO                /* SDWA EXIST?                   */ 00786000
*       &SETDIEOK=ON&               /* SET DIE SUCCESSFUL?           */ 00787000
*       TMCKRETY<=THREE THEN        /* NO-ALREADY TRY 3 TIMES?       */ 00788000
         LTR   SDWAPTR,SDWAPTR                                     0382 00789000
         BZ    @RF00382                                            0382 00790000
         TM    SETDIEOK(DDRPTR),B'01000000'                        0382 00791000
         BNO   @RF00382                                            0382 00792000
         LH    @14,TMCKRETY(,DDRPTR)                               0382 00793000
         C     @14,@CF00306                                        0382 00794000
         BH    @RF00382                                            0382 00795000
*     DO;                           /* NOT YET                       */ 00796000
*       TMCKRETY=TMCKRETY+ONE;      /* UPDATE RETRY COUNT            */ 00797000
         AL    @14,@CF00047                                        0384 00798000
         STH   @14,TMCKRETY(,DDRPTR)                               0384 00799000
*       DERRETRY=ADDR(IGFTMCHW);    /* RETRY TO ISSUE MSG            */ 00800000
         LA    @14,IGFTMCHW                                        0385 00801000
         ST    @14,DERRETRY                                        0385 00802000
*     END;                                                         0386 00803000
*   ELSE                            /* NO                            */ 00804000
*     DERRETRY=ADDR(IGFTMCHR);      /* RETURN TO DISPATCHER          */ 00805000
         B     @RC00382                                            0387 00806000
@RF00382 LA    @14,IGFTMCHR                                        0387 00807000
         ST    @14,DERRETRY                                        0387 00808000
*   RFY                                                            0388 00809000
*     SDWAREG UNRSTD;               /* RELEASE REG 0                 */ 00810000
@RC00382 DS    0H                                                  0389 00811000
*   IF LCLLOCK=ON THEN                                             0389 00812000
         TM    LCLLOCK(DDRPTR),B'00010000'                         0389 00813000
         BNO   @RF00389                                            0389 00814000
*     DO;                           /* IF LOCAL LOCK HELD RELEASE IT    00815000
*                                                            @G24LNLC*/ 00816000
*       RFY                                                        0391 00817000
*        (R0,                                                      0391 00818000
*         R1,                                                      0391 00819000
*         R14,                                                     0391 00820000
*         R15) RSTD;                /*                       @G24LNLC*/ 00821000
*       GEN REFS(PSALITA);                                         0392 00822000
*                                                       /* @G24LNLC*/   00823000
        SETLOCK RELEASE,TYPE=LOCAL,REGS=USE,RELATED=('GOTTEN FOR SUSPE**00824000
                 ND')                                   /* @G24LNLC*/   00825000
*       LCLLOCK=OFF;                /* RESET LOCK HELD INDICATOR   0393 00826000
*                                                            @G24LNLC*/ 00827000
         NI    LCLLOCK(DDRPTR),B'11101111'                         0393 00828000
*       RFY                                                        0394 00829000
*        (R0,                                                      0394 00830000
*         R1,                                                      0394 00831000
*         R14,                                                     0394 00832000
*         R15) UNRSTD;              /*                       @G24LNLC*/ 00833000
*     END;                          /*                       @G24LNLC*/ 00834000
*   RETURN;                         /* RETURN TO CALLER-IGFDE0       */ 00835000
@EL00002 DS    0H                                                  0396 00836000
@EF00002 DS    0H                                                  0396 00837000
@ER00002 BR    @14                                                 0396 00838000
*   END IGFTMCHS;                                                  0397 00839000
*                                                                  0397 00840000

*/*                                                                  */ 00043000
*/*   IGFTMC01: CHECK UCBS FOR MISSING INTERRUPTION                  */ 00044000

         OI    TMC01RTY(DDRPTR),B'00100000'                        0535 01128000
*     END;                                                         0536 01129000
*   ELSE                            /* RETRY MORE THAN 3 TIMES?      */ 01130000
*     DO;                           /* YES                           */ 01131000
         B     @RC00497                                            0537 01132000
@RF00497 DS    0H                                                  0538 01133000

         CLI   ECBCODE(ECBPTR),X'40'                               0538 01135000

*         ECB=ZERO;                 /* RESET THE ECB TO ZERO         */ 01137000

*        (R10,                                                     0541 01146000

*           GPR15P) UNRSTD;                                        0550 01175000
*       END;                        /* ABEND CONTINUED               */ 01176000
*     END;                                                         0552 01177000
*   R14=R4;                         /* RESTORE RETURN ADDR           */ 01178000

*   RFY                                                            0554 01180000

*     R4,                                                          0554 01182000

@RT00315 EQU   NEXTUCB                                                  04272000
